				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Patch Info if you havent seen it yet...<a name="61916"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Sep 14 04 4:23 PM</span></td>
